26
00:01:39,630 --> 00:01:42,400
=Episod 11=

27
00:01:46,780 --> 00:01:48,420
Hebat!

28
00:01:53,270 --> 00:01:53,940
Hebat.

29
00:01:59,844 --> 00:02:00,733
Dia penari yang hebat.

30
00:02:01,830 --> 00:02:02,300
Sesungguhnya.

31
00:02:12,900 --> 00:02:13,790
Menakjubkan!

32
00:02:17,790 --> 00:02:18,900
Dia penari yang menakjubkan!

33
00:02:19,140 --> 00:02:19,860
Wah!

34
00:02:22,070 --> 00:02:23,900
Hebat!

35
00:02:33,830 --> 00:02:35,350
Hebat!

36
00:03:01,670 --> 00:03:07,620
- Cemerlang!
- Syabas!

37
00:03:07,830 --> 00:03:09,740
Tahniah, Encik Ji!

38
00:03:15,510 --> 00:03:16,900
- Hebat!
- Tarian yang menakjubkan!

39
00:03:16,950 --> 00:03:18,230
- Ya.
- Hebat!

40
00:03:18,790 --> 00:03:20,990
Itu bukan tarian Luzhao.

41
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:23,300
Saya pernah lihat sebelum ini. Itu tarian Xilin.

42
00:03:23,700 --> 00:03:25,620
Adakah dia dari Xilin?

43
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:31,460
Dia gadis yang Qiao Manman jumpa

44
00:03:31,550 --> 00:03:32,390
di kampung.

45
00:03:32,644 --> 00:03:33,511
Namanya Fang.

46
00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:34,990
Kenapa dia tak boleh muncul di khalayak ramai?

47
00:03:35,066 --> 00:03:36,510
Ia tak sesuai dengan statusnya.

48
00:03:36,740 --> 00:03:37,270
Bukankah dia

49
00:03:37,270 --> 00:03:39,288
hanya gadis kampung dari luar bandar?

50
00:03:39,670 --> 00:03:40,180
Fang!

51
00:03:40,550 --> 00:03:41,620
Kamu tak boleh buat begitu!

52
00:03:43,230 --> 00:03:44,270
Maksud saya,

53
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,933
tabib tak boleh merawat diri sendiri.

54
00:03:46,022 --> 00:03:48,230
Pernahkah kamu lihat Everything Guild seramai ini

55
00:03:48,350 --> 00:03:49,900
sejak ia dibuka?

56
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:51,350
Ambil ubat ikut arahan ini.

57
00:03:51,355 --> 00:03:51,900
Terima kasih.

58
00:03:51,990 --> 00:03:53,230
Sayang, kamu dah balik.

59
00:03:53,580 --> 00:03:54,900
Gadis ini memang hebat.

60
00:03:59,222 --> 00:04:00,580
Apa nama tarian yang kamu persembahkan tadi?

61
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:02,350
- Tolong ajar kami!
- Kamu memang menawan!

62
00:04:02,350 --> 00:04:02,990
Boleh.

63
00:04:03,460 --> 00:04:04,860
Menarilah bersama saya, kalau begitu.

64
00:04:05,300 --> 00:04:06,110
Baiklah!

65
00:04:06,140 --> 00:04:06,700
Sayang?

66
00:04:09,178 --> 00:04:11,490
(Everything Guild)

67
00:04:13,550 --> 00:04:14,620
Dah balik, Mo?

68
00:04:15,180 --> 00:04:16,180
Majlis dah habis?

69
00:04:16,670 --> 00:04:17,910
Mana menantu saya?

70
00:04:17,940 --> 00:04:18,550
Siapa dia?

71
00:04:19,670 --> 00:04:19,990
Apa?

72
00:04:20,110 --> 00:04:21,300
Beritahu saya siapa dia sebenarnya!

73
00:04:21,820 --> 00:04:23,820
Apa yang kamu maksudkan?

74
00:04:24,350 --> 00:04:25,860
Dia dari Xilin, kan?

75
00:04:34,470 --> 00:04:36,060
Dia bukan orang biasa dari Xilin.

76
00:04:36,550 --> 00:04:38,420
Dia Puteri Xilin, kan?

77
00:04:38,420 --> 00:04:39,266
Rendahkan suara kamu!

78
00:04:46,844 --> 00:04:47,420
Ya, betul.

79
00:04:48,711 --> 00:04:50,200
Apa yang kamu mahu aku buat, ya?

80
00:04:51,910 --> 00:04:53,500
Aku terpaksa lakukannya demi Qiao Manman.

81
00:04:57,030 --> 00:04:59,860
Menyamar sebagai Puteri Xilin adalah jenayah yang boleh dihukum mati.

82
00:05:12,133 --> 00:05:13,800
Aku tak percaya! Ini gila!

83
00:05:13,990 --> 00:05:15,110
Aku dah hilang akal!

84
00:05:15,620 --> 00:05:17,230
Dia Puteri Xilin, dan aku...

85
00:05:26,350 --> 00:05:26,910
Sayang?

86
00:05:28,300 --> 00:05:28,740
Sayang?

87
00:05:29,990 --> 00:05:30,740
Sayang?

88
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:33,860
Kamu tak sihat ke?

89
00:05:41,022 --> 00:05:42,990
Aku ingat fobianya terhadap wanita dah sembuh...

90
00:05:43,466 --> 00:05:44,888
Kenapa tiba-tiba jadi makin teruk?

91
00:05:56,740 --> 00:05:59,110
(Kami dah lama rahsiakan perkara ini daripada dia.)

92
00:05:59,110 --> 00:06:00,977
(Sebenarnya itu memang tak betul.)

93
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:03,666
(Macam mana aku nak berdepan dengan Fang lepas ni?)

94
00:06:05,030 --> 00:06:06,350
Apa yang patut aku buat?

95
00:06:13,138 --> 00:06:16,530
(Manor Liuyun)

96
00:06:16,910 --> 00:06:18,500
Tuanku, saya sudah tahu kebenarannya.

97
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,520
Tabib wanita di Persatuan Everything itu

98
00:06:20,620 --> 00:06:21,990
ialah Puteri Aliya yang sebenar.

99
00:06:22,533 --> 00:06:23,550
Kamu pasti tentang ini?

100
00:06:23,711 --> 00:06:24,755
Tanpa ragu.

101
00:06:26,260 --> 00:06:26,940
Bagus.

102
00:06:27,288 --> 00:06:28,466
Itu sangat baik.

103
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,150
Itu bermakna Permaisuri Jin sekarang

104
00:06:30,150 --> 00:06:31,030
bukan Puteri Aliya.

105
00:06:32,646 --> 00:06:34,930
(Persatuan Everything)

106
00:06:43,030 --> 00:06:44,550
Aku dah balik, Fang.

107
00:06:46,110 --> 00:06:46,940
Mana suami kamu?

108
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:49,260
Aku tak tahu.

109
00:06:49,550 --> 00:06:50,590
Mana abang aku?

110
00:06:51,180 --> 00:06:51,740
Aku tak tahu.

111
00:07:11,350 --> 00:07:12,180
Encik Ji,

112
00:07:13,180 --> 00:07:15,470
Saya datang hari ini untuk ucap selamat tinggal.

113
00:07:17,380 --> 00:07:17,860
Selamat tinggal?

114
00:07:23,088 --> 00:07:25,819
Saya khuatir saya tidak akan dapat menyembuhkan kaki Putera Jin akhirnya.

115
00:07:25,820 --> 00:07:29,180
Bawa Ji Mo dan Fang dan pergi sejauh mungkin dari sini.

116
00:07:29,790 --> 00:07:31,060
Kita akan pergi bersama.

117
00:07:31,910 --> 00:07:32,910
Saya tak boleh.

118
00:07:33,350 --> 00:07:36,180
Itu akan jadi tidak bertanggungjawab bagi saya.

119
00:07:37,820 --> 00:07:38,060
Ya.

120
00:07:39,060 --> 00:07:40,180
Betapa tidak bertanggungjawabnya.

121
00:07:41,066 --> 00:07:41,711
Ini tak boleh jadi.

122
00:07:42,110 --> 00:07:43,230
Saya perlu bercakap dengan Ji Mo.

123
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:48,350
Encik Ji.

124
00:07:48,955 --> 00:07:50,888
Apa yang berlaku antara dia dan abang saya?

125
00:07:51,260 --> 00:07:52,790
Ji Mo telah mengetahui siapa dia sebenarnya.

126
00:07:53,030 --> 00:07:54,990
Sekarang dia rasa dia tak layak untuknya.

127
00:08:02,535 --> 00:08:04,920
(Dewan Hanyuan)

128
00:08:23,620 --> 00:08:24,350
Tuanku.

129
00:08:25,060 --> 00:08:27,820
Saya tidak dapat

130
00:08:28,230 --> 00:08:29,300
tidur langsung kebelakangan ini.

131
00:08:31,940 --> 00:08:32,660
Apa yang berlaku?

132
00:08:33,860 --> 00:08:34,590
Saya asyik terfikir

133
00:08:34,660 --> 00:08:36,860
bahawa tempoh sebulan itu hampir tamat,

134
00:08:37,620 --> 00:08:38,950
dan masih tiada berita baik

135
00:08:39,430 --> 00:08:41,470
dari Kediaman Putera Jin.

136
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:44,470
Saya dihantui kebimbangan.

137
00:08:45,260 --> 00:08:46,660
Saya tak boleh makan

138
00:08:47,230 --> 00:08:48,740
atau tidur.

139
00:08:54,620 --> 00:08:55,380
Tuanku.

140
00:08:58,066 --> 00:09:00,020
Tabib wanita, Bilian, telah meninggal dunia di penjara.

141
00:09:00,933 --> 00:09:02,470
Tabib diraja telah mengesahkan

142
00:09:02,620 --> 00:09:03,660
dia telah diracun.

143
00:09:04,511 --> 00:09:05,555
Tuanku.

144
00:09:05,830 --> 00:09:07,740
Pasti Permaisuri Putera Jin yang melakukannya!

145
00:09:20,110 --> 00:09:21,111
Aduhai.

146
00:09:22,380 --> 00:09:23,500
Tuanku!

147
00:09:23,780 --> 00:09:25,710
Ini teruk! Bangun! Cepat!

148
00:09:26,020 --> 00:09:27,070
Bangun!

149
00:09:28,070 --> 00:09:30,110
Biar saya tidur, boleh tak?

150
00:09:30,190 --> 00:09:31,310
Tidur?

151
00:09:31,330 --> 00:09:33,050
Baginda telah memanggil tuanku ke istana!

152
00:09:34,540 --> 00:09:34,860
Apa?

153
00:09:37,710 --> 00:09:38,830
Tapi belum masanya lagi.

154
00:09:38,866 --> 00:09:39,933
Di mana Tuanku?

155
00:09:39,955 --> 00:09:41,970
Baginda sudah beberapa hari tiada. Tiada siapa tahu ke mana baginda pergi.

156
00:09:41,977 --> 00:09:43,577
Jiufeng pun tak dapat ditemui.

157
00:09:44,110 --> 00:09:45,990
(Fu Chengjin memang tak berhati perut.)

158
00:09:46,260 --> 00:09:48,190
(Saat akhirku pun dia tak muncul.)

159
00:09:48,218 --> 00:09:51,120
(Dewan Hanyuan)

160
00:10:01,844 --> 00:10:03,377
Mengapa Putera Jin tidak ada di sini?

161
00:10:04,260 --> 00:10:04,950
Tuanku.

162
00:10:05,260 --> 00:10:06,430
Putera Jin kurang sihat.

163
00:10:07,310 --> 00:10:08,990
Baginda sedang pulih di kediamannya.

164
00:10:11,182 --> 00:10:11,652
Aliya.

165
00:10:12,950 --> 00:10:14,350
Kita telah bersetuju bahawa kamu akan menyembuhkan

166
00:10:14,950 --> 00:10:16,500
kaki Jin dalam masa sebulan.

167
00:10:18,110 --> 00:10:19,310
Masa itu kini hampir tamat.

168
00:10:21,380 --> 00:10:23,022
Bagaimana keadaan kaki Jin?

169
00:10:27,110 --> 00:10:28,230
Saya gagal.

170
00:10:30,140 --> 00:10:31,740
Tetapi sebelum ini, kamu begitu yakin.

171
00:10:31,740 --> 00:10:33,710
Kamu telah meyakinkan kami bahawa kamu boleh menyembuhkannya dalam sebulan!

172
00:10:37,020 --> 00:10:38,110
Ayah. Ibu.

173
00:10:39,190 --> 00:10:40,350
Kecederaan kaki abang

174
00:10:40,533 --> 00:10:41,740
telah menyeksanya selama bertahun-tahun.

175
00:10:41,780 --> 00:10:42,822
Pemulihan sepenuhnya memerlukan masa.

176
00:10:43,110 --> 00:10:44,710
Tarikh akhir pun belum berlalu.

177
00:10:45,140 --> 00:10:46,230
Bilian sudah pun mati.

178
00:10:46,466 --> 00:10:47,729
Bagaimana jika kita beri dia lebih masa

179
00:10:47,730 --> 00:10:49,290
dan sesuatu terjadi kepada Putera Jin juga?

180
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:52,070
Aliya.

181
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:56,311
Kamu sedar kamu telah melakukan penderhakaan dengan menipu aku?

182
00:10:59,260 --> 00:10:59,710
Ayah.

183
00:11:00,620 --> 00:11:02,110
Saya pernah melawat abang sebelum ini.

184
00:11:02,133 --> 00:11:03,950
Permaisuri Jin sentiasa berusaha keras untuk...

185
00:11:03,950 --> 00:11:04,660
Diam, Yunnuo!

186
00:11:05,488 --> 00:11:07,311
Perkara ini melibatkan kesihatan abangmu.

187
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:08,688
Kamu tidak boleh bercakap sembarangan.

188
00:11:12,177 --> 00:11:13,444
Permaisuri Jin.

189
00:11:14,190 --> 00:11:15,020
Jika Putera Jin

190
00:11:15,470 --> 00:11:17,830
boleh berjalan masuk ke sini dalam keadaan pulih sepenuhnya,

191
00:11:18,190 --> 00:11:19,500
maka kita boleh lupakan perkara ini.

192
00:11:20,380 --> 00:11:21,990
Tetapi jika tidak, maka kamu bersalah

193
00:11:22,860 --> 00:11:24,140
kerana menipu Tuanku.

194
00:11:24,733 --> 00:11:25,780
Penderhakaan boleh dihukum

195
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,380
dengan hukuman mati ke atas seluruh keluargamu.

196
00:11:27,911 --> 00:11:29,866
Adakah kamu fikir kerajaan kecil Xilin

197
00:11:30,540 --> 00:11:32,470
boleh menahan kemarahan Luzhao?

198
00:11:33,260 --> 00:11:33,860
Ibu!

199
00:11:45,470 --> 00:11:45,950
Ayah.

200
00:11:47,350 --> 00:11:48,660
Tiada siapa yang lebih ingin menyembuhkan Putera Jin

201
00:11:48,780 --> 00:11:50,355
melebihi saya.

202
00:11:51,660 --> 00:11:52,350
Saya...

203
00:11:55,230 --> 00:11:55,780
bersalah.

204
00:11:56,555 --> 00:11:58,377
Saya bersedia untuk mati demi menebus kesalahan saya.

205
00:11:58,470 --> 00:11:59,000
Baiklah.

206
00:11:59,355 --> 00:12:00,310
Saya akan tunaikan permintaanmu.

207
00:12:01,190 --> 00:12:01,470
Pengawal.

208
00:12:02,710 --> 00:12:04,533
Permaisuri Putera Jin gagal menyembuhkan Putera Jin

209
00:12:04,555 --> 00:12:05,711
dalam tempoh yang telah dipersetujui.

210
00:12:05,950 --> 00:12:06,990
Dia telah melakukan penderhakaan.

211
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,044
Bawa dia pergi.

212
00:12:08,133 --> 00:12:09,466
Campakkan dia ke penjara maut!

213
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:12,660
Putera Jin telah tiba.

214
00:12:13,190 --> 00:12:14,430
Siapa kata permaisuri saya gagal

215
00:12:15,020 --> 00:12:16,350
menyembuhkan kaki saya?

216
00:12:33,704 --> 00:12:38,160
♪Awan membentang tanpa penghujung di langit♪

217
00:12:40,987 --> 00:12:45,378
♪Memandang ke bawah pada mata yang menatap kejauhan♪

218
00:12:46,929 --> 00:12:50,076
♪Masa terus berlalu♪

219
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:53,430
♪Jejak siapakah yang tertinggal?♪

220
00:12:53,732 --> 00:13:00,236
♪Ia lebih dari sekadar keberanian untuk merindui♪

221
00:13:01,809 --> 00:13:05,073
♪Telah ditakdirkan kita tidak dapat bersama♪

222
00:13:05,393 --> 00:13:08,670
♪Mencintaimu adalah satu rahsia♪

223
00:13:09,086 --> 00:13:15,064
♪Takut mengganggumu lalu kau menjauh tanpa henti♪

224
00:13:16,175 --> 00:13:19,473
♪Betapa aku ingin menyelam ke lautan♪

225
00:13:20,049 --> 00:13:22,609
♪Dan beristirahat dengan tenang♪

226
00:13:22,636 --> 00:13:29,560
♪Untuk menenangkan sebab kesakitan hatimu♪

227
00:13:29,855 --> 00:13:34,329
♪Andai segalanya mampu mengatasi segala halangan dan jatuh cinta♪

228
00:13:34,572 --> 00:13:37,218
♪Awan dan laut pun bisa bersatu♪

229
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:39,400
Maafkan saya...

230
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,083
Saya lambat.

231
00:13:44,633 --> 00:13:48,895
♪Jika jarak tidak mampu memisahkan kita dan ia tidak sukar untuk ditanggung♪

232
00:13:48,938 --> 00:13:51,726
♪Air mata kita akan tetap bersama♪

233
00:13:51,890 --> 00:13:53,710
♪Jangan lupa♪

234
00:13:54,523 --> 00:13:57,341
♪Akan cinta ini♪

235
00:13:58,780 --> 00:14:00,236
Dia telah berusaha sehabis baik.

236
00:14:02,500 --> 00:14:03,230
Dia telah menyembuhkan

237
00:14:04,590 --> 00:14:06,110
kaki saya.

238
00:14:16,430 --> 00:14:17,866
Biar ayah lihat kamu betul-betul.

239
00:14:19,710 --> 00:14:21,430
Bagus. Ini sungguh menakjubkan.

240
00:14:23,070 --> 00:14:23,500
Jin.

241
00:14:25,190 --> 00:14:25,990
